ent-RMCWeaponRifleAK4047-name = AK-4047 assault rifle
ent-RMCWeaponRifleAK4047-desc = The SPP equivalent to the M54C Rifle, the AK-4047 is a cheap and reliable substitute. As such, the weapon often winds up in the hands of mercenaries and insurgents. While not as accurate as the M54, the AK-4047 is sturdier than the UNMC weapon. An AK-4047 still works after being thrown off a cliff and left underwater for a month.
